1
00:00:09,078 --> 00:00:09,874
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,219 --> 00:00:18,847
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:19,889 --> 00:00:22,050
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23,726 --> 00:00:26,388
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27,497 --> 00:00:30,125
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:31,835 --> 00:00:34,929
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:35,572 --> 00:00:38,700
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,176 --> 00:00:44,545
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,183 --> 00:00:48,946
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,052 --> 00:00:50,781
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:50,854 --> 00:00:53,186
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54,724 --> 00:00:56,487
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:56,559 --> 00:00:58,459
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:58,528 --> 00:01:00,962
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:02,866 --> 00:01:09,430
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,540 --> 00:01:13,031
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:13,810 --> 00:01:16,677
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,518 --> 00:01:22,815
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,288 --> 00:01:26,812
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:02:27,961 --> 00:02:28,825
Here we go!

21
00:02:29,096 --> 00:02:32,554
I'm gonna take care of
my duties with gusto again today!

22
00:02:32,833 --> 00:02:35,358
Whoa! Mach 5!

23
00:02:35,435 --> 00:02:41,340
<i>A New Chapter Begins.</i>
<i>The Chunin Exam</i>

24
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:00,917
Oh!

25
00:03:01,261 --> 00:03:03,320
Good morning, Sakura!

26
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,036
Hmph!

27
00:03:15,142 --> 00:03:16,803
<i>Oh, not again!</i>

28
00:03:17,344 --> 00:03:18,333
<i>These two...</i>

29
00:03:18,412 --> 00:03:22,212
<i>They've been sort of strange since</i>
<i>we got back from the Land of Waves...</i>

30
00:03:23,250 --> 00:03:26,447
<i>Oh, it's almost uncomfortable...</i>

31
00:03:27,688 --> 00:03:29,952
Hurry up and get here Kakashi Sensei!

32
00:03:30,157 --> 00:03:31,351
Cha!

33
00:03:42,436 --> 00:03:44,961
Well...
Good morning, everyone...

34
00:03:46,073 --> 00:03:48,041
Today I got lost.

35
00:03:48,508 --> 00:03:49,236
Hey!

36
00:03:51,211 --> 00:03:54,009
Hey, hey...
Kakashi Sensei!

37
00:03:54,147 --> 00:03:57,583
Our Group Seven always has
the easy missions lately!

38
00:03:57,718 --> 00:04:02,280
Aren't there more exciting
missions where I can be more active,

39
00:04:02,356 --> 00:04:06,759
where I can use my Way of the Ninja
and my soul... you know?

40
00:04:07,060 --> 00:04:08,322
Oh yes yes...

41
00:04:09,062 --> 00:04:11,462
I basically understand what
you're trying to say.

42
00:04:17,271 --> 00:04:18,704
<i>Shoot!</i>

43
00:04:19,072 --> 00:04:21,836
<i>He's always making me</i>
<i>indebted to him</i>

44
00:04:21,909 --> 00:04:24,377
<i>and making himself look good</i>
<i>during our missions!</i>

45
00:04:24,678 --> 00:04:26,771
<i>I won't lose, no way!</i>

46
00:04:31,785 --> 00:04:33,275
<i>You little...!</i>

47
00:04:36,123 --> 00:04:38,182
<i>Today for sure!</i>

48
00:04:47,367 --> 00:04:51,463
<i>Hmm...</i>
<i>You are so much trouble!</i>

49
00:04:52,973 --> 00:04:55,305
That's what I'd like to say!

50
00:04:55,676 --> 00:04:59,112
Hey! What're you doing, Naruto?
We're going on our mission!

51
00:04:59,246 --> 00:05:00,440
Okay!

52
00:05:00,547 --> 00:05:02,515
You've been so annoying for a while!

53
00:05:14,594 --> 00:05:17,119
I'm not gonna lose to Sasuke!

54
00:05:26,606 --> 00:05:27,573
Hey you!

55
00:05:27,674 --> 00:05:28,368
What?

56
00:05:29,109 --> 00:05:30,542
Oh, Mrs!

57
00:05:30,744 --> 00:05:32,837
I've gotten rid of all the weeds!

58
00:05:33,814 --> 00:05:34,508
What?

59
00:05:34,581 --> 00:05:35,605
What's wrong?

60
00:05:36,316 --> 00:05:39,581
Those... those aren't weeds.

61
00:05:39,853 --> 00:05:40,615
Huh?

62
00:05:41,221 --> 00:05:45,749
Those are herbs
I grew in my garden!

63
00:05:45,826 --> 00:05:48,090
Ouch, ouch, ouch!

64
00:06:06,380 --> 00:06:08,405
Somebody... help...!

65
00:06:12,919 --> 00:06:17,253
No way! Free fall!

66
00:06:18,425 --> 00:06:19,187
Huh?

67
00:06:24,164 --> 00:06:25,631
You idiot.

68
00:06:35,809 --> 00:06:36,741
Hey!

69
00:06:36,810 --> 00:06:39,108
TRAP FIELD
DO NOT ENTER
Don't go over there!

70
00:06:41,515 --> 00:06:43,745
Hey! Please stop!

71
00:06:47,621 --> 00:06:48,679
That fool...

72
00:06:49,156 --> 00:06:52,648
Oh no! That's because he
stubbornly chose that big dog.

73
00:06:52,859 --> 00:06:56,454
Hey, hey! Wait a minute,
wait a minute!

74
00:07:02,669 --> 00:07:05,399
That's the trap field over there...

75
00:07:07,507 --> 00:07:08,405
Yikes!

76
00:07:28,962 --> 00:07:31,590
Well! It's because you're so reckless!

77
00:07:31,965 --> 00:07:34,934
Geez, you are so much trouble.

78
00:07:38,638 --> 00:07:40,367
Zazuge!

79
00:07:42,109 --> 00:07:44,942
If you act up any more, I'll finish you!

80
00:07:45,612 --> 00:07:50,345
Mmm...
Teamwork hasn't been good lately.

81
00:07:51,118 --> 00:07:52,415
That's right, that's right!

82
00:07:52,586 --> 00:07:55,111
Sasuke, you're to blame for
the poor teamwork!

83
00:07:55,255 --> 00:07:57,223
You're always attracting attention!

84
00:07:57,757 --> 00:07:59,884
That's you, you idiot.

85
00:08:00,694 --> 00:08:03,527
If you don't want to owe me
big time...

86
00:08:06,066 --> 00:08:08,398
you just need to become
stronger than me!

87
00:08:16,810 --> 00:08:20,337
<i>It seems like they're getting</i>
<i>along worse than before...</i>

88
00:08:28,355 --> 00:08:31,017
<i>Shoot...</i>
<i>This is frustrating!</i>

89
00:08:31,992 --> 00:08:35,291
<i>There're plenty of guys outside</i>
<i>who are stronger than I am...</i>

90
00:08:35,929 --> 00:08:38,659
<i>Always making me go on</i>
<i>this kind of lame mission.</i>

91
00:08:46,540 --> 00:08:48,132
Well then...

92
00:08:49,309 --> 00:08:51,106
Perhaps we should disperse.

93
00:08:51,811 --> 00:08:56,612
I do need to submit a report
about this mission.

94
00:08:57,017 --> 00:08:58,712
Okay, then I'm going home.

95
00:09:00,053 --> 00:09:01,486
Oh! Hey!

96
00:09:01,821 --> 00:09:03,618
Sasuke, wait for me!

97
00:09:08,361 --> 00:09:11,956
Hey, how about...
Why don't you and...

98
00:09:12,165 --> 00:09:16,898
Why don't we work on improving
our teamwork together?

99
00:09:17,170 --> 00:09:19,195
You're just like Naruto.

100
00:09:20,340 --> 00:09:24,071
JUST LIKE NARUTO

101
00:09:24,544 --> 00:09:28,378
If you have time to spend on me,
why don't you practice a Jutsu!

102
00:09:29,816 --> 00:09:33,047
To tell you frankly,
your abilities are less than Naruto's!

103
00:09:33,420 --> 00:09:37,550
LESS THAN NARUTO... CHA!!
<i>Less than Naruto! Less than Naruto!</i>
<i>Less than Naruto! Less than Naruto!</i>

104
00:09:41,561 --> 00:09:42,357
<i>That's right...</i>

105
00:09:43,563 --> 00:09:45,656
<i>It's always that way for me</i>
<i>during every mission.</i>

106
00:09:46,299 --> 00:09:48,460
<i>I'll never be able to really</i>
<i>do anything at all.</i>

107
00:09:49,536 --> 00:09:55,532
Sakura! Just let Sasuke be,
and let's practice together!

108
00:09:58,545 --> 00:09:59,204
Huh?

109
00:10:01,047 --> 00:10:02,480
<i>Sensei disappeared.</i>

110
00:10:03,083 --> 00:10:04,710
<i>Was he being thoughtful?</i>

111
00:10:10,090 --> 00:10:10,784
Huh?

112
00:10:13,827 --> 00:10:16,387
<i>Pretending to be...a rock?</i>

113
00:10:42,322 --> 00:10:46,281
There's no such thing as a perfectly
square rock with perfect holes!

114
00:10:46,493 --> 00:10:48,324
It's totally obvious!

115
00:10:49,763 --> 00:10:51,890
Just what you'd expect from
the man I respect!

116
00:10:51,965 --> 00:10:53,956
You are my rival, aren't you!

117
00:11:05,612 --> 00:11:08,103
Hey! That's too much gunpowder!

118
00:11:13,620 --> 00:11:14,917
With an adult sexiness!

119
00:11:14,988 --> 00:11:17,855
I'm Moegi of the senior class
at Kunoichi Preschool!

120
00:11:17,991 --> 00:11:19,891
I love factoring!

121
00:11:20,327 --> 00:11:21,191
Udon!

122
00:11:21,294 --> 00:11:25,162
The most brilliant Ninja in the village!
Konohamaru!

123
00:11:25,465 --> 00:11:28,559
The three of us together are
the Konohamaru Gang!

124
00:11:28,635 --> 00:11:29,431
Here we are!

125
00:11:31,071 --> 00:11:33,403
I knew it was Konohamaru
and friends.

126
00:11:34,007 --> 00:11:38,273
Huh? Why are you all wearing goggles?

127
00:11:40,146 --> 00:11:43,172
We're just copying what
you used to do, bro!

128
00:11:43,650 --> 00:11:44,674
Oh...

129
00:11:45,819 --> 00:11:47,446
What's with the oh!

130
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:50,489
Your reactions have been
pretty cold these days!

131
00:11:52,292 --> 00:11:54,522
So, did you want something?

132
00:11:54,861 --> 00:11:56,260
See? Cold.

133
00:11:56,329 --> 00:11:59,093
So, leader!
Do you have some free time now?

134
00:11:59,599 --> 00:12:00,827
Nah!

135
00:12:02,335 --> 00:12:04,166
I have to train!

136
00:12:04,471 --> 00:12:08,931
What?! You said you'd
play Ninja with us today!

137
00:12:09,008 --> 00:12:12,000
Oh...? Is that right?

138
00:12:12,812 --> 00:12:13,710
<i>Geez...</i>

139
00:12:14,013 --> 00:12:17,642
<i>If I played with these guys</i>
<i>they would make me hang out all day.</i>

140
00:12:17,951 --> 00:12:21,819
Hmph! Why would a Ninja play Ninja?

141
00:12:28,094 --> 00:12:30,062
W-What is it?

142
00:12:31,231 --> 00:12:33,722
<i>So, abilities less than this guy, huh?</i>

143
00:12:34,534 --> 00:12:38,630
<i>You are making me blush</i>
<i>with those stares...</i>

144
00:12:42,075 --> 00:12:44,475
Naruto, who's she?

145
00:12:47,881 --> 00:12:51,282
<i>She's been staring at him with eyes</i>
<i>like she's gonna kill him!</i>

146
00:12:53,086 --> 00:12:53,882
Oh!

147
00:12:54,587 --> 00:12:57,215
You've been busier
than I thought, bro...

148
00:12:57,290 --> 00:12:57,949
Huh?

149
00:12:58,191 --> 00:12:59,954
Is she your?

150
00:13:02,262 --> 00:13:02,921
This?

151
00:13:05,899 --> 00:13:09,426
Shucks, you guys are
pretty sharp for kids!

152
00:13:09,669 --> 00:13:11,466
No way!

153
00:13:11,971 --> 00:13:12,869
Bro!

154
00:13:17,343 --> 00:13:19,072
What are you doing?!

155
00:13:22,382 --> 00:13:24,111
No! Leader!

156
00:13:24,184 --> 00:13:26,482
His pulse, his pulse...!

157
00:13:30,323 --> 00:13:32,587
You ugly wench! Ugly wench!

158
00:13:37,564 --> 00:13:38,223
Huh?!

159
00:13:44,437 --> 00:13:45,495
Nooooo!

160
00:13:55,482 --> 00:13:56,312
Hmph!

161
00:13:59,753 --> 00:14:02,278
Are you all right, Konohamaru?

162
00:14:04,024 --> 00:14:06,458
Oweee...

163
00:14:07,995 --> 00:14:12,625
Darn that broad foreheaded ugly wench!
Is she a girl for real?

164
00:14:24,644 --> 00:14:26,043
Yikes!

165
00:14:44,865 --> 00:14:46,127
That hurt...

166
00:14:46,566 --> 00:14:47,430
- Huh?
- Huh?

167
00:14:54,274 --> 00:14:56,572
So, I have formally received
the report from you.

168
00:14:58,145 --> 00:15:01,774
Is Naruto getting along with the others?

169
00:15:02,149 --> 00:15:02,808
Hmm?

170
00:15:04,284 --> 00:15:06,582
Well, he's doing okay.

171
00:15:07,054 --> 00:15:09,045
I've been busy lately.

172
00:15:10,624 --> 00:15:14,219
I haven't had a chance to see him
even once since his return.

173
00:15:15,262 --> 00:15:16,593
I'm a little concerned...

174
00:15:19,699 --> 00:15:24,363
As you know, Iruka Sensei,
Sasuke is also in our squad,

175
00:15:24,905 --> 00:15:27,772
and Naruto sees him as a rival,
which is a little straining.

176
00:15:28,475 --> 00:15:32,707
But, the result is that his abilities
are developing significantly.

177
00:15:33,613 --> 00:15:35,046
Almost to the point that
he might reach yours,

178
00:15:35,115 --> 00:15:35,945
the one he respects!

179
00:15:37,017 --> 00:15:38,211
I see...

180
00:15:53,934 --> 00:15:54,901
<i>I wonder what it is?</i>

181
00:15:57,637 --> 00:15:58,399
<i>Shoot!</i>

182
00:15:59,239 --> 00:16:00,797
<i>Right now?</i>

183
00:16:10,250 --> 00:16:11,410
<i>These guys...</i>

184
00:16:12,152 --> 00:16:13,244
Konohamaru!

185
00:16:14,821 --> 00:16:16,982
That hurt, little punk!

186
00:16:17,958 --> 00:16:21,621
Stop that. You'll get yelled at later!

187
00:16:22,028 --> 00:16:24,826
I'm sorry...
I was fooling around...

188
00:16:25,799 --> 00:16:27,699
<i>What are these two?</i>

189
00:16:28,335 --> 00:16:31,202
Hey stop!
Let go of that hand!

190
00:16:32,606 --> 00:16:36,098
<i>Huh! So these are Leaf Village's Genin...</i>

191
00:16:36,843 --> 00:16:40,574
Let's play with them before
the strict one comes around.

192
00:16:43,583 --> 00:16:45,210
Let go!

193
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:49,011
You're pretty lively,
you little punk...

194
00:16:56,763 --> 00:16:58,890
You jerk!

195
00:17:10,010 --> 00:17:11,944
Wha?!
What was that?

196
00:17:12,746 --> 00:17:16,876
Leaf Village's Genin are
weaker than I thought.

197
00:17:18,185 --> 00:17:20,016
<i>T-These guys are foreign...</i>

198
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:22,085
<i>Why are they here?</i>

199
00:17:24,457 --> 00:17:25,549
Konohamaru...

200
00:17:26,927 --> 00:17:28,189
Konohamaru!

201
00:17:28,895 --> 00:17:29,884
Konohamaru!

202
00:17:31,531 --> 00:17:33,897
It... It hurts...

203
00:17:37,904 --> 00:17:42,136
Hey! If you don't let go of him,
I won't forgive you! You fool!

204
00:17:43,643 --> 00:17:44,871
You're the fool!

205
00:17:45,412 --> 00:17:47,141
What are you gonna do
by getting him worked up!

206
00:17:48,949 --> 00:17:51,281
You're ticking me off.

207
00:17:51,851 --> 00:17:55,287
I-I don't like little runts anyway.

208
00:17:56,022 --> 00:17:56,750
On top of that,

209
00:17:56,823 --> 00:17:58,882
you're a smart aleck for
someone younger than me.

210
00:18:01,261 --> 00:18:03,058
Makes me want to break him.

211
00:18:09,169 --> 00:18:10,898
It's not on me.

212
00:18:11,771 --> 00:18:14,797
<i>What's with this guy?</i>
<i>He's crazy...</i>

213
00:18:15,942 --> 00:18:19,935
Well, after this little squirt,
it's the little runt that won't shut up!

214
00:18:21,781 --> 00:18:22,805
You!

215
00:18:29,823 --> 00:18:30,482
Huh?

216
00:18:36,329 --> 00:18:39,423
What do you think you're doing
in someone else's Village, you...

217
00:18:42,335 --> 00:18:44,303
Sasuke!

218
00:18:49,643 --> 00:18:51,270
<i>He's pretty cute.</i>

219
00:18:52,212 --> 00:18:53,440
Bro!

220
00:18:55,615 --> 00:18:57,708
Another little punk to tick me off!

221
00:19:01,421 --> 00:19:02,285
Get lost!

222
00:19:05,925 --> 00:19:08,223
Wow! So cool!

223
00:19:11,498 --> 00:19:14,365
Naruto, you're lame!

224
00:19:14,734 --> 00:19:19,034
S-Stupid! I would've quickly
taken down that thug too!

225
00:19:19,105 --> 00:19:19,799
Hmph!

226
00:19:20,173 --> 00:19:22,505
<i>Sasuke, you!</i>

227
00:19:23,143 --> 00:19:27,045
<i>Why're you always,</i>
<i>always meddling like this!</i>

228
00:19:27,847 --> 00:19:30,281
Hey, come down here,
you little punk!

229
00:19:33,553 --> 00:19:38,786
You're the kind of smart aleck
little punk that I despise the most.

230
00:19:41,261 --> 00:19:43,525
Wait! You aren't thinking of
using Crow, are you?!

231
00:19:51,805 --> 00:19:54,069
Kankuro, stop that.

232
00:19:54,574 --> 00:19:55,097
Huh?

233
00:20:03,350 --> 00:20:05,147
You're an embarrassment
to our village.

234
00:20:09,923 --> 00:20:11,652
G-Gaara...

235
00:20:13,193 --> 00:20:16,526
<i>When did he get next to me?</i>

236
00:20:18,164 --> 00:20:20,223
<i>It's stealthy footsteps</i>
<i>on the level of Kakashi...</i>

237
00:20:29,976 --> 00:20:33,036
There is no other reason to
summon you here other than...

238
00:20:33,279 --> 00:20:35,543
As I assume you already understand,

239
00:20:35,615 --> 00:20:37,810
based on the faces
you can see around...

240
00:20:39,085 --> 00:20:41,417
So it's already that time...

241
00:20:42,255 --> 00:20:45,383
The other Lands have already
been notified, right?

242
00:20:46,259 --> 00:20:48,659
I've seen them here and there
in the village.

243
00:20:49,629 --> 00:20:51,460
And, when will it be?

244
00:20:52,532 --> 00:20:54,363
In a week...

245
00:20:55,135 --> 00:20:57,262
That's very sudden.

246
00:21:02,409 --> 00:21:05,401
Now... I will make the
formal announcement.

247
00:21:06,112 --> 00:21:07,807
Seven days from today...

248
00:21:07,981 --> 00:21:13,942
On the first day of July,
the Chunin Exam will begin!

249
00:22:51,920 --> 00:22:53,148
Yes, yes, yes!

250
00:22:53,221 --> 00:22:54,882
It's the Chunin Exam,
it's the Chunin Exam!

251
00:22:54,956 --> 00:22:58,448
If I were to win first place or something,
becoming a Hokage would be closer!

252
00:22:58,526 --> 00:23:00,756
There's no way I can lose!

253
00:23:00,895 --> 00:23:02,726
Konohamaru, you think so too, right?

254
00:23:02,964 --> 00:23:04,056
What?

255
00:23:04,132 --> 00:23:07,659
Who the heck snatched up Moegi,
and what're you gonna do?

256
00:23:07,869 --> 00:23:09,837
Stop, I won't let you get away!

257
00:23:10,438 --> 00:23:13,430
Next time:
"Identify Yourself: Powerful New Rivals"

258
00:23:13,742 --> 00:23:16,677
As for me, I'm gonna kick butt again!
